    {
      "name": "convert_i21_for_inm",
      "docs": [
        "Convert I21 tokens to INM tokens.",
        "",
        "Flow:",
        "1. User transfers `amount` of I21 from their ATA to the treasury I21 ATA.",
        "2. Program mints INM to:",
        "- user's INM ATA",
        "- dead wallet INM ATA (burn portion)",
        "",
        "Using:",
        "- `conversion_rate`: how many INM per 1 I21",
        "- `burn_bps`: burn percentage in basis points",
        "- `max_supply`: maximum total INM supply"
      ],
